libs.content:
find_library (pnetcdf_libraries
  names pnetcdf
  hints ${pnetcdf_lib_hint} path_suffixes lib lib64)

find_program(cythonize_executable
    names cythonize-${python_version_major}.${python_version_minor} cythonize3 cythonize cythonize.bat
    hints ${_python_path})

find_program(clangformat_executable names clang-format
                                          clang-format-15.0
                                          clang-format-14.0
                                          clang-format-13.0
                                          clang-format-12.0
                                          clang-format-11.0
                                          clang-format-10.0
                                          clang-format-9.0
                                          clang-format-8.0
                                          clang-format-7.0
                                          clang-format-6.0
                                     doc "clang-format executable")

find_library (netcdf_library names netcdf
  hints "${netcdf_dir}" "${netcdf_lib_hint}" path_suffixes lib lib64)

deps.context: project(phonon version 48   description "fix phonon post-processor"   languages cxx c)
project(tricubic version 1.1 description "tricubic library" languages cxx)

libs.content:
find_library(cuda_cudart
  names cudart
  path_suffixes lib64 lib/x64
)

find_library(cuda_cudart
    names cudart
    path_suffixes lib64/stubs lib/x64/stubs
  )

find_library(cuda_nvtoolsext_library
      names nvtoolsext64_1 nvtoolsext64 nvtoolsext
      paths env nvtoolsext_path
            env cuda_path
      path_suffixes lib/x64 lib
    )

find_program(cudatoolkit_nvcc_executable
  names nvcc nvcc.exe
  paths env cuda_path
  path_suffixes bin
)
find_library(amd_hip_library amdhip64 paths env rocm_path path_suffixes lib)
find_library(hsa_runtime_library hsa-runtime64 paths env rocm_path path_suffixes lib)
